The project is about helping users understand the basics of online safety through simple interaction conversation.
When the program starts, it will play a greeting audio and display an ACSII logo.

Video: https://youtu.be/Cfo5imyzknY

The setup of the system: Open visual studio (if you dont have, install it), you required to choose the project that you want to see.
(Select the projects name). Once its fully loaded in. select F5 to run the program.

The users will be able to chat to the bot by typing safety related questions such as phishing, password and web browsing.
Here are the commands to say to the bot: How are you
                                         Purpose
                                         Password
                                         Phishing
                                         Browsing
                                         Malware
                                         Privacy
                                         Wifi
The functionalities that are present:
1.Display of ASCII logo
2.Greeting audio
3.Chatbot responses

